---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - CyberAi Network">
  <main>
    <div class="doc-container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: February 5, 2026</p>

      <section>
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>
          CyberAi Network is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you interact with our platform.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3>GitHub Integration</h3>
        <p>
          When you use CyberAi through GitHub Actions or our AI agents, we may access:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Repository metadata (names, descriptions, URLs)</li>
          <li>Code content for analysis and security scanning</li>
          <li>Workflow run information</li>
          <li>Issue and pull request data</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Usage Analytics</h3>
        <p>
          We collect anonymous usage statistics to improve our services:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Feature usage patterns</li>
          <li>Performance metrics</li>
          <li>Error logs (anonymized)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide and improve CyberAi services</li>
          <li>Perform security audits and vulnerability scans</li>
          <li>Generate code suggestions and automated fixes</li>
          <li>Analyze system performance and reliability</li>
          <li>Communicate important updates and security alerts</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Encrypted data transmission (TLS 1.3)</li>
          <li>Limited data retention periods</li>
          <li>Access controls and authentication</li>
          <li>Regular security audits</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Code analyzed by CyberAi is processed in memory and not permanently stored unless explicitly configured by you.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>CyberAi integrates with:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>GitHub</strong>: Repository hosting and CI/CD</li>
          <li><strong>OpenAI</strong>: AI-powered code analysis (when configured)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Please review the privacy policies of these services as they have their own data handling practices.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access your data</li>
          <li>Request data deletion</li>
          <li>Opt-out of analytics</li>
          <li>Export your configuration</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Open Source</h2>
        <p>
          CyberAi is open source software. You can review our code, data handling practices, and contribute improvements on <a href="https://github.com/SolanaRemix/CyberAi" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Significant changes will be communicated through our GitHub repository and documentation.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          For privacy-related questions or concerns, please:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Open an issue on our <a href="https://github.com/SolanaRemix/CyberAi/issues">GitHub repository</a></li>
          <li>Review our <a href="/docs/security">Security Policy</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    margin: auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .doc-container {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: #888;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  section {
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    color: var(--accent-dark);
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--gray-dark);
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #555;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  ul {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #555;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  li {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  strong {
    color: var(--gray-dark);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .doc-container {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
